    <sect1 id="wigl">
        
        <title>What is Gentoo Linux?</title>

        <para>
        Gentoo Linux is designed for the developer, power user and enthusiast.
        Incorporating the latest sources and technologies (such as ReiserFS and the
        Portage system), Gentoo Linux was created to provide the ultimate Linux
        experience. If you've tried all the other distros and you're still not satisfied,
        then you need to experience Gentoo.
        </para>

     </sect1>

